'''Gev-Toosa''' was a settlement at [[Stend IV]].

Gev-Toosa was the biggest settlement on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]], but it was only big enough to be considered a village. It had no [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceport]]; approaching [[Starship/Legends|ships]] received a pre-recorded message suggesting them to land outside Gev-Toosa and walk to the town.

The [[Army of Life]] wanted to transport dangerous [[clodhopper]]s to Stend IV, where they would spread havoc and devastate the colony. It was its goal "the biggest settlement on Stend IV".

However, the [[Jedi Council/Legends|Jedi Council]] discovered the Operation, and they sent [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Dree-Tekes]] there, where she would [[Showdown on Stend IV|fight]] the Army hired agents. Dree-Tekes met with four [[Gran/Legends|Gran]] militiamen and provided them with blaster carbines, an old heavy blaster cannon and a grenade launcher.

